<h1>兴业视点<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span></b></h1>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.6pt;

<h2>恶化的经济数据继续冲击市场<u style='text-underline:black'><span style='text-underline:
black;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none'> </span></u></h2>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:26.35pt;line-height:103%'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>11</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#3F3F3F'>月<span lang=EN-US>CPI </span>同比增长<span lang=EN-US>2.4%</span>。 </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>国务院国资委、财政部昨日联合发出通知，从四个方面对国有控股上市公司股权激励做了进一步补充规定。
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:26.45pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>点评： </span></p>

KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>11</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:99%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>月<span lang=EN-US>CPI</span>同比增长<span
lang=EN-US>2.4%</span>，比上月回落<span lang=EN-US>1.6</span>个百分点，其中食品价格同比增速较上月回落<span
lang=EN-US>2.6</span>个百分点，非食品价格同比增速也较上月回落<span lang=EN-US>1.6</span>个百分点。物价回落的速度十分快，<span
lang=EN-US>11</span>月<span lang=EN-US>CPI</span>涨幅创<span lang=EN-US>2006 </span>年<span
lang=EN-US>11</span>月份以来新低，<span lang=EN-US>11</span>月<span lang=EN-US>PPI</span>涨幅也创<span
lang=EN-US>2006</span>年<span lang=EN-US>4</span>月份以来的新低。<span lang=EN-US>11</span>月物价涨幅快速下滑的原因，除国内需求萎缩供方压力加大，以及货币增速持续回落之外，还有一个重要的扰动项。<span
lang=EN-US>2007 </span>年<span lang=EN-US> 11 </span>月份，发改委上调电价和成品油价格，也使得<span
lang=EN-US>2008</span>年<span lang=EN-US>11</span>月份，<span lang=EN-US>CPI</span>构成中车用燃料以及居住用水、电、燃料价格涨幅较<span
lang=EN-US>10</span>月份大幅下降。 </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:5.3pt;margin-bottom:4.8pt;
margin-left:5.35pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:103%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'><span
style='mso-list:Ignore'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><![endif]><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>物价快速下跌表明经济在急剧收缩，通货紧缩风险显现。可以预期，需要更为扩张的货币政策，实际上物价的下跌也为更大力度的降息提供了空间。因此，在坏数据的负面冲击下和流动性并不十分充沛的情况下，市场可能颇为震荡，但是扩张政策预期之下，并非毫无机会，建议投资者注重波段操作。
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:9.5pt;
margin-left:26.35pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
"Times New Roman";color:#414141'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<h1 style='margin-bottom:1.25pt'>分析师观点<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
</span></b></h1>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:5.35pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:
宋体;color:#2C4155'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.1pt;
margin-left:5.1pt;text-indent:-.5pt'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#2C4155'>【<span
lang=EN-US><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span></span>调研速递<span
lang=EN-US><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span></span>】 </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:5.1pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.5pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;
color:#2C4155'>z</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
Arial;color:#2C4155'> </span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2C4155'>公路行业研究员<span lang=EN-US><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#2C4155'>王爽<span lang=EN-US><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span></span>（<span
lang=EN-US>021-68419393-1207</span>） </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.45pt;
margin-left:5.35pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2C4155'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<h2>广深铁路（<span lang=EN-US>601333</span>，￥<span lang=EN-US>5.10</span>，推荐）调研信息速递<u
style='text-underline:black'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
"Times New Roman";color:black;text-underline:black;text-decoration:none;
text-underline:none'> </span></u></h2>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:26.35pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>今天我们调研了广深铁路，与公司董秘和证代进行了座谈。 </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:26.45pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>点评： </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>广深铁路是我国唯一的铁路客运上市公司，也是我国盈利能力最好的客运路段。公司经营稳健，但当前也看不到发展的机遇。
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>公司以客运为主，占总收入的<span
lang=EN-US> 58%</span>，主要包括广深城际动车、港九直通车和长途车，其中最主要的是广深城际动车。 </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>当前，广深城际每天平均发行<span
lang=EN-US>86</span>对，运行时间为<span lang=EN-US>6-24</span>点，平均上座率<span lang=EN-US>80%</span>。春运期间，运行图安排为<span
lang=EN-US>120</span>对，距离饱和运能仍具有一定空间，比如可以通过延长通车时间和进行动车连排等方式提高客运量。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>二等座票价全程<span lang=EN-US>75</span>元，一等为<span
lang=EN-US>95</span>元，而公路客运为<span lang=EN-US>65</span>元，为了维持对公路的竞争优势以及从交通管理角度，发挥节能环保优势，吸引更多客流到铁路，我们认为票价上调可能不大。该线路未来分流风险较大，广深港客运专线将于<span
lang=EN-US>2011</span>年通车，定价未知，对高端客流的分流存在。 </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>据了解，当前广东民工返乡较多，<span
lang=EN-US>4 </span>季度长途客运的客流有所增长。由于在春运期间，铁路处于供不应求状态，我们认为该情况会刺激公司四季度客运收入增长。但对明年的客流量，我们认为可能会小幅下滑，公司盈利变化情况也取决于公司对运行班次的调整。
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>公司货运主要为铁矿石和煤炭等大宗物资，我们对明年的运量持谨慎态度，悲观情况下存在下滑可能，认为增幅会在<span
lang=EN-US>-10-5%</span>之间。 </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>对公司的外延增长方面，主要取决于国家相关部委对铁路的定位和铁路的盈利模式如何制定，涉及范围较广，现在还说不清楚。
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.85pt;
margin-left:26.35pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>综上，我们预计公司<span lang=EN-US>08-10</span>年<span
lang=EN-US>EPS</span>为<span lang=EN-US>0.20</span>、<span lang=EN-US>0.21</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>0.24</span>元，鉴于公司业绩较为稳定，给予推荐评级。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:5.35pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:
宋体;color:#2C4155'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:5.35pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:
宋体;color:#2C4155'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.1pt;
margin-left:5.1pt;text-indent:-.5pt'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#2C4155'>【<span
lang=EN-US><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span></span>信息点评<span
lang=EN-US><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span></span>】 </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:5.1pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.5pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;
color:#2C4155'>z</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
Arial;color:#2C4155'> </span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2C4155'>银行行业研究员<span lang=EN-US><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#2C4155'>王倩（<span lang=EN-US>021-68419393-1027</span>） </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.4pt;
margin-left:5.35pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2C4155'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<h2 style='margin-right:.9pt'>银行业营业税制改革空间讨论（<span lang=EN-US>“</span>推荐<span
lang=EN-US>”</span>，维持）<u style='text-underline:black'><span style='text-underline:
black;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none'> </span></u></h2>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#3F3F3F'>2008</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>年下半年，内外经济环境恶化，实体需求下降趋势确立，宏观调控从紧缩到结构放松最终转向全面放松，银行作为政策调控，尤其是货币政策执行的最重要渠道，既要权衡自身市场化经营中的盈利增长和资产质量，又要承担刺激经济、引导流动性的通道作用。在经济急速转型过程中，保护政策通道，稳定金融体系的呼声越来越高，金融税改成为市场关注的焦点。
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#3F3F3F'>2008</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>年，所得税率从<span lang=EN-US>33%</span>下降到<span
lang=EN-US>25%</span>，为银行贡献了<span lang=EN-US>15%</span>左右的净利润增速，部分缓解了经济下行周期中，拨备回升以及资金回流给银行带来的压力。
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>所得税红利释放后，营业税具备相对较大的<span
lang=EN-US>“</span>红利空间<span lang=EN-US>”</span>。根据<span lang=EN-US>2008</span>年三季报，银行业平均营业税率为<span
lang=EN-US>5.96%</span>，明显高于<span lang=EN-US>A</span>股全部公司<span lang=EN-US>3.14%</span>的平均水平。
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>我们认为，未来不排除银行营业税制改革的可能性。自<span
lang=EN-US>2000</span>年以来，非银行上市公司的平均营业税率从<span lang=EN-US>1.16%</span>小幅上升至<span
lang=EN-US>2.83%</span>，而银行业平均营业税负率（以营业税金及附加<span lang=EN-US>/</span>营业总收入粗略计算）则一直徘徊在<span
lang=EN-US>4.5%-6%</span>之间，与非银行企业相比，银行业营业税率有下降空间。 </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>由于有效所得税率和金融往来利息收入差异，降低营业税对各家银行净利润贡献不一。根据我们的测算，按照受益幅度由大到小，各家上市银行排序如下：华夏、深发展、民生、浦发、宁波、中信、交行、兴业、工行、建行、中行、招行、北京、南京。其中每降低营业税率<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>个百分点，将使得华夏、深发展、民生、浦发、中信、交行、兴业的净利润各增长<span lang=EN-US>4.9%</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>3.6%</span>、<span lang=EN-US>3.3%</span>、<span lang=EN-US>2.7%</span>、<span
lang=EN-US>2.4%</span>、<span lang=EN-US>2.3%</span>、<span lang=EN-US>2.2%</span>。
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.2pt;
margin-left:4.6pt;text-indent:20.5pt;line-height:103%'><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:103%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'>无论营业税制改革是否能在近期推出，我们认为，旨在刺激经济复苏的宽松政策，尤其是货币政策将引导流动性释放至实体经济，而作为政策通道的银行，将迎来规模扩张的机会，前期不断内流的资金为未来的规模扩张做好了准备，维持行业评级为<span
lang=EN-US>“</span>推荐<span lang=EN-US>”</span>。 </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.05pt;
margin-left:5.35pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2C4155'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:5.1pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.5pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;
color:#2C4155'>z</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
Arial;color:#2C4155'> </span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2C4155'>煤炭行业研究员<span lang=EN-US><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#2C4155'>刘建刚（<span lang=EN-US>021-68419393-1050</span>） </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.4pt;
margin-left:5.35pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2C4155'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:

color:#414141'>亿元，双方持股比例分别为 </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>55</span><span

</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:

105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#414141'> </span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;

style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;
color:#2C4155'>z</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
Arial;color:#2C4155'> </span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2C4155'>造纸行业研究员<span lang=EN-US><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#2C4155'>雒雅梅（<span lang=EN-US>021-68419393-1207</span>） </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.45pt;
margin-left:5.35pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2C4155'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<h2 style='margin-right:.05pt'>太阳纸业（<span lang=EN-US>002078</span>，￥<span
lang=EN-US>8.55</span>，推荐）向下修正业绩预告点评 <u style='text-underline:black'><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black;
text-underline:black;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></u></h2>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.3pt;
margin-left:26.2pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:
-.5pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>公司发布 </span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>08
</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:
105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:
KaiTi;color:#414141'>年业绩预告修正公告：将 </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>08 </span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#414141'>年全年业绩由之前预计的增长 </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>30%-50%</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#414141'>向下修正为小于 </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>30%</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#414141'>。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:26.2pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:-.5pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>点评：</span><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:
105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#414141'> </span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:26.2pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:-.5pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>业绩向下修正符合预期。主要原因在于本轮全球金融危机对行业的冲击。</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:5.35pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>从市场面看，行业景气上半年到达峰顶，</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#414141'>7 </span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>月份下 </span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>8
</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:
105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:
KaiTi;color:#414141'>月份行业景气见顶，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>9 </span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#414141'>月份纸品价格出现松动，十一长假后，一些经销商出现恐慌性抛售带动市场价格一泻而下，截至当前，纸价下跌幅度已经在达到 </span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#414141'>20% </span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>左右。就公司覆盖纸品而言，跌幅最深的为白纸板，达 </span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#414141'>26%</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>，其次是白卡和铜板纸，跌幅为 </span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#414141'>20%</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>，双胶纸跌幅最小，为 </span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>17%</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#414141'>。同时，原材料价格也在 </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>10 </span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#414141'>月份后上演了瀑布试的大跳水，短短一个多月时间，下跌</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:5.85pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:-.5pt;line-height:105%'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>50%</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#414141'>以上。</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
"Times New Roman";color:#414141'> </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:26.2pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:-.5pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>从业绩来看，此次金融危机主要从 </span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#414141'>3 </span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>方面对业绩产生影响：</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>
</span></p>

  KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>以上，这两个纸种均是当前下滑幅度较大的品种，导致公司投资收益大幅下降。第三季度公司已经出现投资亏损
  </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;

  KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>元。第四季度在下游需求继续萎缩和企业主动性减产的情况下，我们预计亏损将更为严重</span><span

  <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:-.2pt;margin-bottom:

  inter-ideograph;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:109%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3'><![if !supportLists]><span

  mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'><span
  style='mso-list:Ignore'>（3）<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></span></span><![endif]><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
  11.0pt;line-height:109%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
  KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>自制浆变成业绩的<span lang=EN-US>“</span>拖累<span
  lang=EN-US>”</span>。公司于 </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
  mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:109%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
  mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>2 </span><span
  style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:109%;
  font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:
  KaiTi;color:#414141'>月份投产的 </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
  mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:109%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
  mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>13 </span><span
  style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:109%;
  font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:
  KaiTi;color:#414141'>万吨化机浆原本是我们十分看重的一个<span lang=EN-US>“</span>卖点<span
  lang=EN-US>”</span>，但是在浆价出现 </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
  mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:109%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
  mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>50%</span><span
  style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:109%;

  KaiTi;color:#414141'>以上巨幅下跌的情况下，当前看来，该项业务已经由业绩的<span lang=EN-US>“</span>加分<span
  lang=EN-US>”</span>因素变成为<span lang=EN-US>“</span>减分<span lang=EN-US>”</span>因素。我们粗略测算当前公司自制浆业务已经濒临亏损的边缘，毛利率已由前期的
  </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
  line-height:109%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
  "Times New Roman";color:#414141'>25%</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;

  KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>附近，净利率接近 </span><span

  KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>数据公布后，市场在权重股的带动下股指逐波反弹，但午后调整幅度加大，股指一路震荡下行，最终两市均收在全天低点位置。截至收盘，沪指报下跌
  </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;

  "Times New Roman";color:#414141'>1.72</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;

  mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>％，两市成交量基本与前日持平，略有下降。行业方面，以金融股为主的指标板块未能延续升势，全天低位疲弱整理，对股指形成拖累；此外，由于昨日闭幕的中央经济工作会议表示要发挥房地产在扩大内需中的积极作用，地产股表现相对抗跌；而前日活跃的新能源、</span><span
  lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:
  104%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";

  style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:104%;
  font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";

  KaiTi;color:#414141'>周四沪深两市基指跟随股指震荡下行。截至收盘，沪基指下跌 </span><span lang=EN-US

  102%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
  color:#414141'>2.98%</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:

  KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>；成交量方面，沪市小幅放大，深市有所萎缩。从周四基金净值表现来看，净值跌幅靠前的均为前期加仓或被动型投资基金，此外以
  </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;

  color:#414141'>06 </span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
  11.0pt;line-height:102%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
  KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>年前成立的基金为主，相比之下，次新基金反倒相对抗跌。封闭式基金方面，高折价大盘封基跌幅较小，此前涨幅较大的基金则出现一定回调。随着中央经济工作会议的结束，我们认为，此前指导性意见的具体化、政策化将成为下一阶段行情的主要推动力。我们坚持此前观点，建议投资者关注政策面导向，可借助波段参与被动型基金，相比之下增强型指数型基金对于收益和风险的把握可能更加灵活。各类型基金日均净值</span><span
  lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:
  102%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
  color:#414141'>/</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
  line-height:102%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
  mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>价格涨跌幅具体如下：</span><span
  style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:102%;
  font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
  color:#414141'> </span></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
  margin-left:21.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
  10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;

  style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:5.1pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.5pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;
color:#2C4155'>z</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
Arial;color:#2C4155'> </span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2C4155'>汽车机械行业研究员<span lang=EN-US><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#2C4155'>朱学东（<span lang=EN-US>021-68419393-1043</span>） </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.7pt;
margin-left:5.35pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#3F3F3F'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<h2 style='margin-right:.05pt'>飞瀑三叠<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
"Times New Roman"'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b>撷取浪花朵朵<b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>――</span></b>汽车行业 <b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>2009 </span></b>年度投资策略<b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><u style='text-underline:black'><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
text-underline:black;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none'> </span></u></b></h2>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:5.35pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>我国汽车业理论上还有很大空间，但工业化初期积累的消费人群需求释放后，由于收入差距的巨大使得第二次浪潮的发生尚需时日。</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:5.35pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>海外经济衰退、收入水平的下降和预期的变坏，判断０９年将出现负增长，但考虑到国内经济还能保持６％以上的增速，下降幅度不会很剧烈。</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:5.35pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>在整体下降过程中，选择一些下降幅度不大的细分行业和相关公司，以谋求相对收益。相对看好中高级轿车和大中客车生产企业。</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:26.2pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:-.5pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>行业评级：观望</span><span style='font-size:
10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'> </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:26.2pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:-.5pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>重点推荐公司：一汽轿车、宇通客车、宁波华翔</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.25pt;
margin-left:5.35pt'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#2A447D'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:5.1pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-.5pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;
color:#2C4155'>z</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
Arial;color:#2C4155'> </span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2C4155'>石化行业研究员<span lang=EN-US><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#2C4155'>方磊（<span lang=EN-US>021-68419393-1014</span>） </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:5.35pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:#2A447D'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:47.2pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:25.7pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:97.45pt;line-height:105%'><u style='text-underline:#2A447D'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#2A447D'>机会渐行渐近</span></u><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><u
style='text-underline:#2A447D'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#2A447D'>――</span></u></b><u
style='text-underline:#2A447D'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2A447D'>石化行业 </span></u><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal'><u style='text-underline:#2A447D'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#2A447D'>2009 </span></u></b><u
style='text-underline:#2A447D'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#2A447D'>年度投资策略</span></u><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#414141'>国内石化行业在 </span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>08 </span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#414141'>年经历了最困难的时期后，</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>09 </span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;
color:#414141'>年将呈现见底回升的态势。</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
"Times New Roman";color:#414141'> </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:26.2pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:-.5pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>国际油价已经大幅下跌到合理范围内，短期内可能会继续探底，但长期依然看涨。</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:
.3pt;margin-left:5.35pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:105%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;
mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>国内能源价格改革步伐将加快，中石油、中石化的价值将逐渐和油价正相关，其长期投资机会可能会随油价的见底而出现，我们认为这个时点可能会出现在
</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;
line-height:105%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:
"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>09 </span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:"KaiTi",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:KaiTi;mso-bidi-font-family:KaiTi;color:#414141'>年的下半年。</span><span
style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#414141'>
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:4.55pt;margin-bottom:

</span><span style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:

</span></p>
